00:00:16.065 --> 00:00:19.050
So let's take a look at
Apple's website as an example,

00:00:19.050 --> 00:00:20.460
if I scroll down here,

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:23.265
you can see that these
elements fade-in.

00:00:23.265 --> 00:00:24.795
I'm going to scroll down.

