00:03:25.789 --> 00:03:29.105
And once it's triggered,
this square moves.

00:03:29.105 --> 00:03:31.910
But what if I want to
animate the trigger itself?

00:03:31.910 --> 00:03:33.215
We can do that as well.

00:03:33.215 --> 00:03:36.095
