element trickier.

00:03:36.095 --> 00:03:39.635
And we can say, if the user
hovers over these elements,

00:03:39.635 --> 00:03:41.840
these elements
should change, e.g.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:44.090
it should grow, it should move,

00:03:44.090 --> 00:03:47.270
it should fade out
anything you can imagine,

