00:03:51.904 --> 00:03:53.075
So in this case,

00:03:53.075 --> 00:03:55.655
the trigger itself is animated.

00:03:55.655 --> 00:03:57.335
I'm going to show
you another example.

00:03:57.335 --> 00:04:00.035
If I click on this square
